Beat 32 ounces of softened cream cheese in the electric mixer or by hand. Whip until smooth and creamy. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c9/Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/c/c9/Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet1.jpg/aid2880885-v4-728px-Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Add 1 cup of granulated sugar and 1 tsp. of vanilla to cream cheese and mix well. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/80/Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/8/80/Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/aid2880885-v4-728px-Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Add 4 eggs to mixture. Consider cracking the eggs into a separate bowl before sliding them into the cookie cake batter to avoid adding a bad egg or shells. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/39/Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/3/39/Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet3.jpg/aid2880885-v4-728px-Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Whip 1 cup of sour cream and a pinch of salt to the batter. You can also add cookie crumbs to batter, about 6-8 crushed or fine ground. Mix until all ingredients are well combined. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/17/Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet4.jpg/v4-460px-Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/1/17/Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet4.jpg/aid2880885-v4-728px-Make-Oreo-Cookie-Mini-Cheesecakes-Step-3Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
